ght of the select window https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon/pull/5485 \r\n\r\n### Desired UX and success metrics\r\nCreate designs that allow the user to navigate to a specific page without incrementally clicking the forward and back pagination nav arrow.\r\n\r\n### Considerations:\r\n- [ ] Error message\r\n- [ ] Always require a value\r\n- [ ] The behavior when the number entered is greater than the number of pages (Reset to the highest page?)\r\n- [ ] What other components have this type of input inside a toolbar or component? What needs to be established for this type of pattern? \r\n\r\n### Exploration\r\nNumber input specs that are similar to the mobile ipnut component.\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19270502/75998210-18278480-5ec6-11ea-82cd-2654701a228f.png)\r\n\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/5546/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":1,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/carbon-design-system/carbon/issues/5546/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"score":1}]}}